name: MIke Schulte
text: It either closed or not open yet... Need to make this clear on here.

name: Joel Mills
text: Fresh and ready to eat when I'm ready. Cooked the kids pizza first. Then the wife and I eat 40 mins later. We were not ready like the kids. Crust is great also very good. Love the fact you pay no tax! Will be getting my pizza's from here for now on. Great job Papa Murphy's!

name: Dennis Spellman
text: Great customer service. Nice people. Great Pizza.

name: Ronald Quiballo
text: Great tasting pizza and fresh toppings.  Coming here really helps out when I haven't had time to think of something for dinner.  The large Pappa's Perfect is my family's go to.

name: Gary Douglas
text: The service is quick and friendly. The selection of salads and pizza is great, not to mention the drinks and desserts that are also available. The location is prime and quickly accessible.

name: 魏宏展
text: store is clean, and staffs are warm, kind, and fast.

name: Nathaniel W.
text: Good price. Decent pizza. Variety of gourmet toppings like artichokes and sun dried tomatoes.

name: sleebus jones
text: Pretty much Papa Murphy's is the only pizza I eat anymore.  Thin crust + cooking it on a pellet grill is bliss!

name: Krystal Johnston
text: Great pizza and customer service!   Love this place!

name: Ashley Ross
text: We come here often. They are always fast and curtious except the staff at the Spring Green Blvd location in Katy, worse customer service ever, they caused my 5 star to change to 1 star!

name: Laura Bongfeldt
text: Staff was friendly and my order was on time!
